# 💻 C / C++ Exercises

This folder contains **C and C++ programming exercises** ranging from basic syntax to data structures.

## 📚 Topics Covered
- Basic syntax (variables, loops, conditionals)
- Functions and pointers
- Structures and dynamic memory
- Classes (C++) and OOP concepts
- Algorithms and data structures

## ▶️ How to Compile and Run
For **C**:
```bash
gcc program.c -o program
./program
